{"tid":2091833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"連儂牆襲擊案 男生脫罪  官斥警供詞現三版本：矛盾誇大難接受","createTime":"2020-07-03T01:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T15:21:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c08660aea9e0c8fd17df44bf55d2f442ae6f82","tid":2091833,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:41:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/Y567HBYBGT5CTDVW2KRDLOBXEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FY567HBYBGT5CTDVW2KRDLOBXEQ%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=590ba92e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FY567HBYBGT5CTDVW2KRDLOBXEQ%2F&h=11208390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/Y567HBYBGT5CTDVW2KRDLOBXEQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆襲擊案 男生脫罪 <br />\n官斥警供詞現三版本：矛盾誇大難接受<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年7月，有人在天水圍行人隧道內建立連儂牆，其間一名休班警長跑步經過時舉機拍攝，與現場人士爭執，事後報稱遭一名17歲男生用雨傘襲擊。案件經審訊後，裁判官昨裁定涉案男生普通襲擊罪名不成立，更直指警長庭上說法、書面供詞與案發影片嚴重不一致，使案情出現三個版本，證供矛盾及誇大，令人難以接受。辯方指警長涉嫌作假證供，問法庭會否轉介予律政司跟進，惟裁判官只稱「警方自己考慮」。<br />\n<br />\n徐姓男學生（17歲）被指去年7月31日在天水圍天秀路行人隧道內襲擊休班警長X。旁聽席上聲援者昨聞判後鼓掌，男生庭外表示無法形容脫罪心情，「只係我好彩贏咗，唔代表個司法制度係公正」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/O0d6tMGnnvcowlcYsJx0GriTQuE=/865x608/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/23NQBG65WC7YCDPY7GLWNUTX6Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FO0d6tMGnnvcowlcYsJx0GriTQuE%3D%2F865x608%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F23NQBG65WC7YCDPY7GLWNUTX6Q.gif&h=67d234dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告徐姓男學生昨被判襲擊罪名不成立，當庭獲釋；右圖為案發行人隧道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無如實交代案情<br />\n<br />\n裁判官葉壠亮<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n令他感到疼痛。<br />\n<br />\n惟根據X的書面<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n市民才介入協助。<br />\n<br />\n葉官再指，<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n但影片顯示其視線多次離開被告。<br />\n<br />\n葉官續指，面對辯方質疑，X僅回應稱「不清楚」及「不知道」，甚至聲稱影片經剪接，卻無法指出刪剪之處，可見X只是為矛盾證供自圓其說。<br />\n<br />\n由於X的證供嚴重不一致，葉官認為他並無如實交代案情，更在辯方盤問下將庭上及書面供詞一併推翻，甚至修正遇襲時間及位置。葉官認為，控方舉證不能達至毫無合理疑點。<br />\n<br />\n另外，一名13歲女生被指去年10月31日在旺角藏有100條索帶，而一名14歲男生則被指去年11月9日在旺角廣華街管有一條60厘米膠管。兩人分別被控管有工具意圖作非法用途罪。據了解，控方昨同意撤控，兩人獲准自簽1,000元、守行為18個月。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC2171/19、<br />\nWKCC700011、700015/20"},{"pid":"a595fe34bfed24f92045e09fc5cf4966d3f5a42e","tid":2091833,"uid":179409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:03:18.000Z","msg":"無讀書<br />\n作故仔能力係差啲"},{"pid":"a80596250f0b1e623c8373cc1a6a84eafaf778ee","tid":2091833,"uid":102700,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:05:40.000Z","msg":"唔係話有幾個版本<br />\n證明無夾口供咩"},{"pid":"f474a2f59f0f64ff3be1955bf9e3b13364088e92","tid":2091833,"uid":54959,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"吓？明顯無夾口供證明係誠實喎，點判㗎？"},{"pid":"849e6f4548cb14a392f691896f95ae55af42129a","tid":2091833,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:11:13.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會員標籤功能 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a>"},{"pid":"5078dd793a4fc2a51f05ea5a9719e5e124fb41eb","tid":2091833,"uid":10998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:13:02.000Z","msg":"黃官又放生<br />\n明明多個版本證供就係冇夾口供=誠實可靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e383370b20ef831544f73d0b8cdc03144348b0","tid":2091833,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:14:07.000Z","msg":"er 。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},